title: * The List of All Active Datasets in this ERDDAP *
summary: This dataset is a table which has a row of information for each dataset currently active in this ERDDAP.

title: IOOS ATN Contact Database
summary: Extracted contact information from the Hopkins Marine Lab ATN data dump. This is useful when looking up contact information by an event_id

title: IOOS ATN Trackline Database from Core 1 Dump from the Stanford Block Lab
summary: Animal tracklines as a product of processing and cross referencing data in the Core 1/2 IOOS ATN databases
